wiki.summary: “Nakamura” pays homage to Shinsuke Nakamura, a heavily respected and decorated pro wrestler signed to the WWE. The song samples Nakamura’s theme song, “The Rising Sun,” on which the beat is based upon. Uzi’s floating hums make up a larger proportion of this song, creating an almost majestic and cinematic experience for their listeners. "I wanted to get in the ring, I was ready to get in the ring" They have also hinted at making an in-ring debut at WrestleMania 40 in their hometown of Philadelphia. Read more on Last.fm.
